    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Past the Moon; Towards the Sun</strong> is a solo developed, contemporary fantasy, kinetic visual novel that invites you into a tale of self-discovery and empowerment. Step into the shoes of Colleen, a self-conscious young woman forced into a hidden magical world, where she must confront her doubts and learn to trust the power she was taught to suppress.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013160/extras/7b6a129caf4b96f671435e8d990319ba.poster.avif?t=1766433967\" width=750 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013160/extras/7b6a129caf4b96f671435e8d990319ba.webm?t=1766433967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013160/extras/f52753c7d79b8183a1c68c35ba601dde.avif?t=1766433967\" width=400 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the magical world of Erue, a land not too dissimilar to our own, where magic is said to be gifted to humanity from the stars above. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once praised as a talented child, Colleen Avery grows into a self-conscious young woman who no longer believes her magic is enough to shape her future. When a strange man dressed like a rat abducts her for reasons he refuses to explain, Colleen is forced into a journey far beyond anything she imagined.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along the way, she encounters vampires, werewolves, and assassins; some willing to help, others bound by their own hidden motives. As secrets unravel and danger closes in, Colleen must learn to trust herself, her companions, and the magic she was taught to suppress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by classic fairy tales and modern fantasy, <i>Past the Moon; Towards the Sun</i> is a story of self-worth, mystery, and the quiet courage it takes to believe in yourself when the world does not. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013160/extras/66cfef73be6fc3fbe9f4a9d7abd76f06.poster.avif?t=1766433967\" width=750 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013160/extras/66cfef73be6fc3fbe9f4a9d7abd76f06.webm?t=1766433967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013160/extras/9a30a65036884ac46724e0213ef5427d.avif?t=1766433967\" width=400 height=65 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story driven kinetic visual novel</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No romantic paths</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Focus on narrative, atmosphere, and character growth</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No adult or eroge content</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013160/extras/c9a38bd74d6af5eda2345ede80f8351d.poster.avif?t=1766433967\" width=750 height=285 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013160/extras/c9a38bd74d6af5eda2345ede80f8351d.webm?t=1766433967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013160/extras/cc01c0f8f6805d997de8221a68cd78b7.avif?t=1766433967\" width=400 height=65 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 40 chapters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approx. 180,000 words</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Live2d character animations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voice Acting <i>(Efforts/Exertions)</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A contemporary fantasy world inspired by classic fairytales</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013160/extras/20d577d601e6cf384445534b20708173.poster.avif?t=1766433967\" width=750 height=273 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013160/extras/20d577d601e6cf384445534b20708173.webm?t=1766433967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
